{"tid":2043154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"栗戰書3提「非和平方式」不放棄武統台灣 美國防部：有能力超越並擊敗對手","createTime":"2020-05-30T08:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T10:05:16.000Z","uid":239336,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e42e09e9f0ac21b3162cf57be8a2a47ffe9241","tid":2043154,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"（新增內容）全國人大通過制訂「港版國安法」後，北京當局再以《反分裂國家法》警告台灣。《人民日報》今日刊出全國人大委員長栗戰書昨日出席「反分裂國家法」實施15周年座談會發言全文，3次提到「非和平方式」的字眼，強調「中共沒有放棄武力統一」。隨着台海威脅升級，美國國防部官員於當地時間29日表示，美軍有防範各種可能衝突的準備，如果中國國家主席習近平下令中央軍委採取攻擊行動，美國要確保接到命令的人「對是否能執行這個命令心中有所疑慮」。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）周四在發Tweet警告：「從中國共產黨對香港所做的事可以得到兩個啟示：第一，他們會簽署幾乎任何協議，因為當他們認為有需要時，就會毀棄他們所作的承諾；第二，他們今日在香港所做的，就是他們接下來想對台灣做的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200530/FFG3LGSSHWLTNSTMVU6MTYUOQY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200530%2FFFG3LGSSHWLTNSTMVU6MTYUOQY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=29e4d801\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200530%2FFFG3LGSSHWLTNSTMVU6MTYUOQY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=78390d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200530/FFG3LGSSHWLTNSTMVU6MTYUOQY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a>"},{"pid":"a7b18f855a528ca29868aea0d851fb7408aa62b8","tid":2043154,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}